Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.00,0:01:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第六十七話\N神秘劍士 天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.77,0:01:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 烤熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.57,0:01:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.21,0:02:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好吃的樣子\N我開動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.35,0:02:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得趁熱吃呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的呀\N少嘍嗦 臭小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼 剛剛寄到的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.76,0:02:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 是信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,京都寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是小操啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.06,0:02:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦？那個黃鼠狼姑娘\N還會寫信啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.07,0:02:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前也有寄來哦 像這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的有點不一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她說京都發生恐怖的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.92,0:02:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖的事件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.09,0:02:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死者是順著河水漂下來的\N身份很快就查出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.06,0:02:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以前的幕府大人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼名門世家有錢人\N會落得那個模樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.00,0:02:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是這樣 更可怕的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.84,0:03:03.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死者身上\N被書上像咒文一樣的字或圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.81,0:03:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,背上被刻上奇怪的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.48,0:03:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是誰 又是為了什麼目的\N而殺死他的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.15,0:03:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切都被謎霧包圍\N京都街頭巷尾都在談這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.56,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託 求求你 錢我願意出\N多少錢我都願出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.00,0:03:33.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫先生你是前御庭番的頭目\N我需要您的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.34,0:03:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我經由秘密途徑查出\N你是當今京都最厲害的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你仗劍保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.11,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我說幾次你才懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.55,0:03:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人現在無心戰鬥\N就算是閻羅王來哀求也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.82,0:03:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我收到預告函呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.36,0:03:57.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道河上發現的屍體吧\N上面寫下次要我入地獄呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.86,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰發出那種東西的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.93,0:04:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之我不相信警察\N蒼紫先生 拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.07,0:04:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論你有什麼理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我都不打算拿劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.48,0:04:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.71,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爺爺 你認為到底是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.51,0:04:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是南蠻語吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.15,0:04:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,南蠻語？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.78,0:04:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前幾天發現的遺體上刻有文字\N就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:05:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然我不是很瞭解\N我想應該是葡萄牙荷蘭文吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.73,0:05:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說下手的是南蠻人嘍？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.56,0:05:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恩…這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.27,0:05:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,調查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.27,0:05:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.71,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可能是某件想像不到的\N大事件的開端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.79,0:05:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,查出眉目了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.35,0:05:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.32,0:05:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何那麼慌張 小操不在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.96,0:05:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說查出什麼眉目了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經歷250年歲月復仇時刻來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.34,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始是川接下來是滿月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.21,0:05:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後白晝死亡\N轉變成黑暗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神子將會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.31,0:06:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個圖案是江戶時代初期\N天主教徒所使用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.82,0:06:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來被禁止\N不准公開的印記
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.16,0:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別太莽撞…小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有種就出來看看\N我要看你是什麼樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,視情況而定 我會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快保護我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.83,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白尉先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.31,0:09:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要求見緋村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.38,0:09:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去京都？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.35,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蒼紫大人請你盡快趕去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我陪你們一起 請準備吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.84,0:09:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去京都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.85,0:10:00.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今早第三人的預告\N寄到你手上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.89,0:10:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.33,0:10:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經…完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.26,0:10:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知道為什麼你會被找上嗎\N你應該知道原因吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.30,0:10:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經完蛋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.04,0:10:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別吊人胃口了 我性子很急的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.84,0:10:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下手人是誰\N只要告訴我這點我就打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就這麼簡單 你還不懂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是以前葡萄牙傳教師寫的書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.43,0:10:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寫的全是外國字\N這我怎麼可能看得懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.84,0:10:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三人的復仇\N在書死亡的時刻發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.94,0:10:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝死亡 轉變回黑暗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.11,0:10:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神子將會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.06,0:11:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.00,0:11:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.31,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老闆 老闆 老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.13,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛剛去見過小操了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她還很虛弱\N但是很快就會恢復的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.47,0:11:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為身體並沒受到傷害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.04,0:12:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那…到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.88,0:12:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小操的心被射穿了…\N被一束光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.18,0:12:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那一夜\N他的劍的閃光射中小操
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是過去從未見到的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心的一方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心的一方？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者是…類似的絕招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.94,0:12:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用劍氣攻擊對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.67,0:12:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,使對手身體\N陷入無法動彈的狀態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.74,0:12:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否真的如此就不曉得了\N只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.15,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個晚上 死在那個屋邸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.05,0:12:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有收到預告的當事人\N葛西而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.16,0:12:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他人每個都跟小操一樣\N身上無傷的昏倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.80,0:12:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕都是受到外人\N以劍背快速擊昏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.24,0:13:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說…好像…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.07,0:13:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是我特意來找你來的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.98,0:13:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拔刀齊 那劍法不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說是飛天御劍流？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.85,0:13:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.52,0:13:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼 飛天御劍流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且他的拔刀速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.30,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毋庸質疑 絕對是超神速的快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.10,0:13:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了\N我再也不想聽你瞎猜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.54,0:13:39.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他實力可能與你相當\N不 搞不好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.18,0:13:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好…搞不好是指什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.95,0:13:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好超越劍心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.22,0:13:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,越越劍心？\N沒那種人吧他又不是神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 除了神 沒有別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.70,0:14:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.31,0:14:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會…世上不該有種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.61,0:14:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我相信的人只有劍心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.56,0:15:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙真是\N每次都帶來麻煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.93,0:15:09.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連個見面禮都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.03,0:15:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,見面禮？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.50,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般人至少會帶一升酒來\N你這麼大了還不曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你期待我這種事是沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.11,0:15:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經不期待你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.11,0:15:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就請你別再抱怨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.29,0:15:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早就知道你會過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.26,0:15:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近一再發生的殺人騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.72,0:15:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神秘的圖案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.33,0:15:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及被人誤以為\N是神的飛天御劍流的劍手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯 終於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.03,0:15:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該來的時刻來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說 師父你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.75,0:16:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的真正身份是天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.42,0:16:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.12,0:16:10.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被讚美為\N天草四郎再世的天主教徒劍客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.38,0:16:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他到底會在什麼時候出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.35,0:16:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝死亡 轉換為黑暗的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.68,0:16:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝死亡…\N這到底是什麼意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.16,0:16:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼神之子 什麼爛預言了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.16,0:16:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全是胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世上最強的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.14,0:17:02.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事要從幾十年前說起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.85,0:17:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要從我的上一代…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.28,0:17:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是第12代\N比古清十郎的時代說起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.05,0:17:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個備受期待可能繼承\N13代比古清十郎之名的弟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.96,0:17:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他名字是仁志田兵衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.76,0:17:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是藤兵衛沒有通過\N繼承飛天御劍流的最後考驗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.31,0:17:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徒弟必需以天翔龍閃\N來破解理師父的九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.35,0:17:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失敗的話只有死路一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.88,0:17:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也曉得 那是御劍流的規定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.16,0:17:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤兵衛失敗 墜入瀑布死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.47,0:17:59.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是十幾年後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.34,0:18:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有個消息傳來說\N藤兵衛在大陸活得好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.54,0:18:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實他還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.48,0:18:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.98,0:18:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 藤兵衛應該\N已經是七十歲的高齡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.78,0:18:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是這個故事還有下文的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.23,0:18:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,後來才知道\N仁志田兵衛是天主教徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.67,0:18:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是隱藏的天主教徒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.37,0:18:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 那裏有信仰自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.31,0:18:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他從日本流浪到那裏\N那裏可說跟天堂一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.75,0:18:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後十幾年後 他回來日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.62,0:18:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶著一位被稱為「神」的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.12,0:18:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他帶著報仇之心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.62,0:18:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想讓那男人成為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.52,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解救飽受欺壓的\N日本天主教徒的偉大領導者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.21,0:19:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個男人14歲就會超神速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也攻破了藤兵衛\N使出的九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.22,0:19:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破解九頭龍閃的絕招\N那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.86,0:19:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤兵衛沒有傳授\N飛天御劍流的資格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.09,0:19:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是那男人\N能破解藤兵衛的九頭龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.03,0:19:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想他使的招式應該就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天翔龍閃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.85,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,森林太過安靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.12,0:19:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小鳥們…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動物們是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,寬永十四年的島原之亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.83,0:20:11.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候創造許多奇跡的\N天草四郎所佩戴的傳說之劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藤兵衛將那把劍送給了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.17,0:20:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我還不瞭解他想幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.54,0:20:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是真的凡人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.75,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是神之子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.78,0:20:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他的名字叫做天草翔伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報仇的時刻到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.86,0:20:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝死亡\N轉變為黑暗時神之子將會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.08,0:21:02.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 好怪的天氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白晝在…死亡了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是！！

